{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ee0e3fbf-d75d-49f7-81d6-c0e589c296a6","content":"No repo-specific pipeline files to reference, so here's a general guide:\n\n### Migrating from `VSTest@3` to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n**1. Update your test project (`.csproj`):**\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Opt in to the new test runner -->\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nEnsure you're on **MSTest 3.3+** (which bundles the platform runner).\n\n**2. Replace `VSTest@3` in your pipeline YAML:**\n\n```yaml\n# Before\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    resultsFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n**3. Publish results & coverage:**\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish TRX results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n> For Cobertura output, add the NuGet package `coverlet.collector` **or** use `--collect \"Code Coverage;Format=Cobertura\"` (requires the Microsoft Code Coverage collector).\n\n**Key differences:**\n- `dotnet test` drives the new platform runner directly — no separate test adapter discovery needed.\n- TRX and coverage are handled via `--logger` and `--collect` arguments.\n- Use `condition: always()` on publish steps so results appear even on test failure.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bf96cf87-fc21-40b6-931f-4030f35aeea7","outputTokens":561,"requestId":"1BC1:23CF76:20EEE7D:245348C:6A03CEB9"},"id":"0e670f6a-a749-48e9-b607-97430e54ab59","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:07:18.098Z","parentId":"9ccc7cea-8cf2-46c6-8001-dae3d1738d95"}
